profile:
Singular Focus:

Most landscape and renovation companies try to serve many types of customers at the same time; homeowners, shopping centers, office buildings, golf courses, and the list goes on. They are pulled in all directions trying to be everything to everyone. At Captain Handy Co, we focus on one customer, you, the homeowner. We have a singular focus on bringing you the best landscaping and interior renovation, the best customer service, and the best value for your home. When you consider that quality renovation can improve the value of your home by 10%-15%, why wouldn’t you hire the one company that focuses specifically on residential landscaping? We are Your Residential Landscape and interior renovation Company.
Easy:

Our business makes your life easier. We are committed to improving the quality of life for our customers so they can spend their time on other things. Our customers are busy and have hectic lives. They do not have time to deal with different companies for lawn care, mowing, design, patio building. Captain Handy Co. offers turn-key solutions to your landscape needs. One call connects you with one of our very qualified Landscape Advisors who will make sure that you are delighted with your landscape. It is that easy.
Hassle-Free:

Ever notice how some companies make it a hassle just to do business with them? Who needs hassles? Life is complicated enough as it is. With Captain Handy Co, you can expect fast response times, clear and concise proposals, and work to be done how and when we promise it would be. You can also expect us to stand behind our work, show up when we say we will and take care of the little things that can take a landscape,renovation and experience, from blah to wow! We take away the hassles so all you have to do is enjoy your landscape.
Professional:

With 5 years under our belts, we know a thing or two about being the professional contractor of choice. Our staff has an average tenure rate of over twelve years, and some team members have been with us for over two decades! They undergo extensive and on-going training to not only assure that your renovation looks fantastic, but also to make sure that you are treated superbly. Our staff members are clearly recognizable in their sharp uniforms so you will know who is on your property. With so many companies claiming to be “professional”, isn’t it nice to work with a company that actually is?
Our Values:

At Captain Handy Co, we provide Tender Loving Care to both you and your interior and landscape renovation. These are our Values:
•	Treat people honestly, fairly and with respect in all situations
•	Create a comfortable environment in which to work and do business
•	Be open to problems and complaints, and work quickly to a fair resolution
•	Present a professional image and working safely
•	Have a “can-do” attitude
•	Stand behind our commitment to quality and service
•	Be active, responsible and positive citizens in the communities in which we work

Welcome to On Time Contracting.  I've had my renovation business now for 15+ years.   I do one job at a time to finish on-time and on-budget.  When you hire me, I'm your contractor and I'm there each day from start to end.  Call Today For FREE ESTIMATE.  

I do both interior and exterior renovations.  In the summer, I do decks & fences, porches, custom sheds and cabanas.  I also do interior renovations in fall / winter including kitchens, bathrooms, basements and additions.

Professional Decking and Fencing Installation
​
Operating in GTA, we offer full decking and fencing services for residential and commercial purposes with the best quality and workmanship at affordable prices. 

EXCELLENCE IN WORKMANSHIP

We provide a professional and customer-friendly outdoor carpentry service that adds style to your home. profile:
My name is Erik Tibor and I am the owner and operator of Sweet Home Construction. I would first like to thank you for taking the time to read a bit about our company.

 At Sweet Home Construction we are a close-knit and family-built company that strive to provide our customers with an exemplary experience and flawless finished projects so they can be proud of their decision to entrust their current and future projects with us.

 We at Sweet Home Construction specialize in fences, interlocking, deck building, basement renovation and repair. We also are able to offer assistance on many other construction or renovations projects not listed upon request.

I started this company twelves years ago after realizing that there was a need for general contractors that were able to get projects done with great care, on time and on budget after going through many aches and pains with other contractors when trying to renovating my family home.  With the help and support of my family we were able to complete my family home for my parents.

Since then,I have added many trusted workers to my growing team to fulfill other projects for many businesses both large and small as well as families working to improve their living spaces.

 At Sweet Home Construction we believe that our commitment to superior quality and results will allow us to continue to take on larger projects and leave more smiles on the faces of those who see the results that we produce.

We are social:

Express Fence is a company that is focused on subdivision MULTIPLE fence projects. Our office team will work hard to get all your neighbours on board and site team will provide best workmanship to complete your fence project on time.  We build more than 15,000 ln ft of fence every year and this number is growing rapidly with hundreds of satisfied customers.

■ Unlike industry standards, we provide best estimated completion time for your project
■ We can purchase high quality material with low cost because of subdivision volume
■ Our experienced teams will complete your project with high standards and meet project deadlines
■ We provide 5 year workmanship warranty

We believe providing best customer service and products to our valued customers is our main goal as a company. Our team at the site works hard to bring best possible workmanship and our office team is focused to provide best customer service and best material with low cost possible. 

Our site teams are experienced but they always improve themselves to get better and better every day. Subdivision projects bring us volume on purchasing and we always use this buying power to reduce cost of material. This is how we can provide the best possible price with high quality fence for your home.

profile:
Ap Cons is a modern construction service provider committed to delivering the best and customizable construction services to people in Toronto. We’re a one-stop brand for property owners who desire to get the best value for their resources when hiring experts to meet their construction needs. From clearing and excavation services to home additions and all that falls in between, our team of dexterous professionals can always give you the best.

Having been in the industry for a pretty while, we’ve mastered the rudiments and all it takes to keep every customer smiling in satisfaction. Little wonder our previous clients can’t stop recommending our services and hoisting our brand name in praise. When you think of a construction company you can trust in Toronto for excellent services, Ap Cons is the brand to call.  

What We Do
Here at Ap Cons, we provide a wide range of reliable construction solutions. We strive to be involved in every project we handle from start to finish, offering our clients cost-effective solutions.
Check out our services:

Excavation
Waterproofing
Concrete Work
Home Additions
Interlocking

Ap Cons is a brand that tailors each service to meet the exact needs of each client. So, when you come to us with a project, rest assured that we’ll carve out a process that works in line with your budget, site, requirements and timeline.

profile:
Green Curve Landscape & Renovation was founded 10 years ago. We have completed hundreds of projects specializing in custom built wood fences and gates, commercial/industrial chain link fence installation, post hole digging and setting, custom decks and pergolas, concrete pads, custom interlock stone work. Our versatile trained craftsmen have the technical expertise and experience that will amaze you along with our wealth of satisfied clients. We are a proud Canadian owned company and stand by our warranties, no job is too big or small. We stand behind every projects with professionalism, honesty and satisfaction. We have strong relationships with local manufacturers and suppliers so you will get high quality material at the best price. We are fully insured and WSIB compliant. We are just a few clicks away to provide free estimates 
and expert advice. If you are a savvy homeowner and want to dramatically increase your curb appeal, add value to your home whether its adding a beautiful and elegant deck or pergola to enjoy the summer days or adding privacy and security with a custom built fence or if you are a DIY we can dig and set your fence and deck footings for you. Please contact us bow to help create the oasis of your dreams!

profile:
Palm Tree Pools opened in 2003 to provide a higher class of service in the residential swimming pool market. For all too many pool owners, the pool had become a headache and a burden, and the problems most commonly stemmed from unreliable, uninformed service technicians.

Palm Tree Pools technicians are friendly, knowledgeable, conscientious and reliable. We take pride in our appearance by maintaining clean uniforms and vehicles. We realize that a pool is an extension of one’s home, and may be the focal point of social entertainment, a private retreat for adults or a major part of family recreation.

With this in mind we understand that the water must be clear and inviting, and equipment dependable and efficient.  Water that is not carefully balanced can cause enormous destruction to a pool heating and filtration system in a short amount of time.

Our Swimming Pool Service includes:

    Opening
    Closing
    Liner Replacement
    Leak Detection
    Restoration and Renovation
    Rubber – Swimming Pool Surfacing

We also specialize in the design and installation of driveways, front walks, side walks, patios and steps.
Or work includes the use of:

    Stamped Concrete
    overlayments
    concrete sealing
    repair and maintenance
    rod iron fencing

Turn your traditional backyard into something to talk about. We can renovate an attractive and functional pool that will turn your existing backyard lawn or patio into a delightful backyard escape.

Choose your finely detailed liner from a variety of exciting patterns and colors that allow you to recreate your backyard environment into a private refuge for relaxing or a special place for outdoor entertaining.

Go beyond the basic pool and choose from a variety of special additions and products to complement your pool.

One of our fine spas or dramatic water features can be the perfect finishing touch. Our professional construction crew will carefully redesign your pool and any options you have selected. Once the water is added, you’ll be able to enjoy the view around your pool as well as the time you spend in it!

If you are not happy with your current service provider, or if you are ready to stop worrying about the pool so that you can just enjoy it, call us at today.  From major renovations to a one-time service call, we have the experience, knowledge, and equipment to provide a higher class of customer service.

We also provide reliable Concrete Work using Regular and Stamped Concrete, Overlayments and Spray Coats, the GTA, Toronto, Brampton, Mississauga, and Georgetown areas.

Contact us today!
